Waarp Gateway Ftp 2.1.5 API Reference

The Waarp Gateway FTP project is a Full Waarp FTP Server with Executor (Gateway) support as Waarp Project: this is an extension of Waarp FTP server with execution support at the end of a transfer.

See:
          Description


Waarp Gateway Ftp Configuration file based loaders package
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.config Exec configuration.

 

Waarp Gateway Ftp Database package
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.database Classes implementing Database access
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.database.data Classes implementing Database Data model
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.database.model Classes implementing Database Model (H2, Oracle, PostgreSQL, MySQL)

 

Waarp Gateway Ftp ControlHandler package
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.control Exec FTP server control business.

 

Waarp Gateway Ftp DataHandler package
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.data Exec FTP server data business.

 

Waarp Gateway Ftp Administrator package
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.adminssl Classes implementing HTTPS Administration support

 

Waarp Gateway Ftp File package
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.file Filesystem based implementation of File, Dir, Auth and SimpleAuth.

 

Waarp Gateway Ftp SNMP package
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.snmp SNMP support classes.

 

Waarp Gateway Ftp Utils package
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.utils Utility classes.

 

Other Packages
org.waarp.gateway.ftp Main class for the Exec FTP server based on Filesystem and simple authentication.
org.waarp.gateway.ftp.service Interface for Apache Daemon tool to run as a Service

 

The Waarp Gateway FTP project is a Full Waarp FTP Server with Executor (Gateway) support as Waarp Project: this is an extension of Waarp FTP server with execution support at the end of a transfer.
